    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently has a severe oil leak and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears, meaning it is not currently reliable for daily driving. The exterior shows heavy wear with several noticeable dents, rusting on the door panels, and fading clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places and the air conditioning is non-functional. This is a project car or a candidate for parts, and we recommend having it towed from the lot.",
