    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, and it still drives super smoothly. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventures, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 28900.0,
