      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example benefits from documented subframe reinforcement and a recent double-VANOS overhaul, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain remains precise. Equipped with the factory M Variable Differential Lock and a firm, communicative suspension setup, the chassis dynamics remain sharp. Finished in Carbon Black over a well-maintained Nappa leather interior, this M3 delivers an authentic, analog performance experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
